{"tid":1171640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國當局急了！警告做空人民幣將「損失巨大」","createTime":"2019-05-26T00:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T00:35:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"11854db6ac3de4a0165e4631d20cc0d0574bd2bb","tid":1171640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"中國當局急了！警告做空人民幣將「損失巨大」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2801702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2801702&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b330bbb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2801702&h=fbc15cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2801702</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰本月初開始愈演愈烈，人民幣大受衝擊，這段期間兌美元匯率貶逾2.5%，距離「破7」的重要關卡越來越近。不過中國銀行保險監督管理委員會（銀保監會）主席郭樹清今日喊話，稱人民幣不可能持續貶值，做空人民幣的投機行為必會遭受巨大損失。<br />\n<br />\n中國今舉辦「金融供給側改革與開放」論壇，郭樹清因未到論壇現場，由銀保監會發言人肖遠企代為宣讀演講稿。<br />\n<br />\n稿中表示，人民幣匯率短期波動是正常的，但中國仍是世界經濟增長的最大引擎，具備極好的市場空間和增長潛力，決定人民幣不可能持續貶值，投機做空人民幣必然遭受巨大損失。<br />\n<br />\n此外，郭樹清也隱隱回擊美國對中國操縱匯率的指控。稿中指出，一直以來發達國家要求人民幣加強匯率彈性，但是當人民幣匯率的市場化程度提高、隨著外部因素出現較大幅度貶值的時候，「有的國家」又對我們無端猜疑指責，這種做法顯然「十分可笑」。<br />\n<br />\n郭樹清也補充，雖然外匯市場近期波動，但中國企業和人民並沒有任何恐慌，因越來越多的人了解靠買賣外匯獲利是不現實的，將金融資產轉移到海外也是不安全的。<br />\n截至發稿，1美元兌6.9002人民幣。"},{"pid":"540e17f297ad8d6095f1fd138a6e3153069326d4","tid":1171640,"uid":193131,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"邊個損失巨大先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accec00feac73eb9f96a0cbf5f469963d422e290","tid":1171640,"uid":50386,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:42:05.000Z","msg":"投機做空人民幣，（支那）必然遭受巨大損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d738477e4ba8aaf91cf19b0317c4bd454e56bf1","tid":1171640,"uid":42188,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">郭樹清也補充，雖然外匯市場近期波動，但中國企業和人民並沒有任何恐慌，因越來越多的人了解靠買賣外匯獲利是不現實的，將金融資產轉移到海外也是不安全的。</span></blockquote>梗係啦，啲人民幣都轉唔到美金，仲點樣轉移到去海外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4c69d53a8204ff721c4e6e5e88b9720ad4acf5","tid":1171640,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:54:12.000Z","msg":"點沽空人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4122cc9f769767cb67c2ea8ff10ea03f1de9973f","tid":1171640,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"唔知一帶一路d 錢銀係用人民幣定美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e29be6ff8bca7614041f8a91275416be3f6ecb","tid":1171640,"uid":171446,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"816df45c5fb47f828b2379b67ed7d65340ce4b8c","tid":1171640,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"實空到"},{"pid":"56be05a843ae6476ec6113c03c046328c51b3bfc","tid":1171640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c87ee1d7b6044314f927fbfb5cc51a681d1464a7","tid":1171640,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96346ca12c5afc3d6c4fa440ebdaf30c043eeda7","tid":1171640,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"收到signal識做啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392dc0600e717437f0328da41081a5d37b90430c","tid":1171640,"uid":254425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,